- The emoji picker layout renders correctly
- The search box has a clear (X) button that works properly
- The "Frequently Used" section and emoji categories render correctly
- The "4 Issues" in DevTools are browser-level issues (form field accessibility, deprecated features) unrelated to the emoji search functionality

